{"tid":967952,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港流感高峯期　四日殺六人","createTime":"2019-01-04T00:32:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-04T01:13:08.000Z","uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"810d05324c80a25a4707fdf601c3d766f4d8abb9","tid":967952,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T00:32:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190104/20583389\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190104%2F20583389&d=lFXb0YqbEbX%2FrCjcQDBsfzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=ed0fbc13\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190104%2F20583389&h=cf8aa6c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190104/20583389</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】本港已踏入流感高峯期，流感四日內<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">殺</span>六人。由去年12月30日至今年1月2日短短四日內，衞生防護中心錄得21宗成人嚴重流感個案，當中六人<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">死</span>亡；感染者有11人屬50至64歲的高<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">危</span>感染群組。之前一周防護中心只錄得13宗成人嚴重流感個案，顯示嚴重個案大幅增加。<br />\n<br />\n男童中招<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">腦病變</span><br />\n衞生防護中心表示，中心與醫管局及私家醫院合作監測錄得，由去年12月30日至今年1月2日有21宗成人嚴重流感個案，感染者中有11人屬50至64歲，即防護中心指的高危感染群組，七人屬65歲或以上，三人屬18至49歲。患者中有12人感染H1甲型流感。<br />\n<br />\n六名死者中有五人是65歲或以上，一人是50至64歲。中心同期錄得一宗兒童嚴重流感個案，患者是一名八歲男童，曾接種預防流感疫苗，病發後出現腦病變。<br />\n<br />\n之前一周（去年12月23日至29日）防護中心只錄得13宗成人嚴重流感個案，當中三人死亡。感染者中有三人已接受預防流感疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n前日各間公立醫院急症室求診人次又再攀升，全日共有6,070人次求診，當中有逾1,000人次要轉送內科病房留醫，令內科病床在午夜時佔用率<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">高達112%</span>。<br />\n■記者陳沛冰"},{"pid":"3de74e5e3836450afe93a68e65fa231b0fab4456","tid":967952,"uid":65346,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T00:33:13.000Z","msg":"以前沙士都無殺咁快啦...樓價未有同步大下跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"291e8c7c66cb811cd4532e7847d794fb24497052","tid":967952,"uid":3177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T00:34:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔舒服戴口罩唔好野開<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46d47a205d6dff772192dbc021383521dcf528d2","tid":967952,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T01:05:50.000Z","msg":"劉德華死左未<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c8b1b89587ca38d5282c30f9510696e5963be75","tid":967952,"uid":198763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T01:07:19.000Z","msg":"年年都有人話流感變種，政府隱瞞疫情<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1687ea2e7208114063810cd00bbd6b267e504f5","tid":967952,"uid":126731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c8b1b89587ca38d5282c30f9510696e5963be75","tid":967952,"uid":198763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T01:07:19.000Z","msg":"年年都有人話流感變種，政府隱瞞疫情<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T01:08:32.000Z","msg":"其他國家無好似沙士咁當香港係疫區. 你死多幾多件廢老都無用."},{"pid":"e2bcbc0f214b1c2084b03888197827cdbfef175d","tid":967952,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46d47a205d6dff772192dbc021383521dcf528d2","tid":967952,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T01:05:50.000Z","msg":"劉德華死左未<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T01:09:18.000Z","msg":"快..."},{"pid":"9b1559d6f5539396cfe7b7dcf6fdd51d203fae53","tid":967952,"uid":140234,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T01:13:08.000Z","msg":"做過內科一定知112%係亂寫<br />\n<br />\n平時一定過130%<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}